Faith-based apparel, jewelry & more ✨
A portion of all profits given 🌎

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elevated Faith on August 18, 2021. May be an image of ring.

node.text: Our B2G1 free ring offer is still live! Add 3 rings to your cart, and you’ll receive the discount automatically 😍 link in bio to shop our rings! 💍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Elevated Faith on August 17, 2021 tagging @olivia_calfee. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
If you could only pick one, would you go with our Do Not Fear blue hoodie or grey hoodie? 🤔💙⠀
⠀
Link in bio to shop the hoodie!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elevated Faith on August 16, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and people standing.

node.text:
It’s our 6th birthday!! 🥳🍰 on the final day of EF, shop 25% off all of our New Arrivals! ✨ link in bio to shop the final day of the sale now.

We’re SO grateful for your support over the years; we truly wouldn’t be in this place without each one of you. Our mission hasn’t changed from day one: to provide conversations starters that open doors for wearers to tell friends and strangers about their faith. Here’s to another year of spreading the Gospel message! 🙏

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elevated Faith on August 15, 2021.

node.text:

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elevated Faith on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'And when I wake up, You are still with me. Psalm 139:18'.

node.text: “How precious to me are your thoughts, God. How vast is the sum of them! Were I to count them, they would outnumber the grains of sand—when I awake, I am still with you.” -Psalm 139:17-18

node.text:
Today's Sale: Hoodies & Crewnecks!! 🤩 Today only, shop 25% off all of our hoodies & crews. Use code 'BIRTHDAYWEEK' at checkout to redeem 🥳⠀
⠀
Fun fact about 2018: We moved our operations into a new warehouse which actually used to be the town grocery store many years before!

On the second day of EF, shop 25% OFF ALL RINGS! 🤩 Use 'BIRTHDAYWEEK' at checkout to redeem ✨⠀
⠀
Fun fact: In 2016, we were shipping all of our packages out of our founder's parent's living room!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elevated Faith on August 10, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch and jewelry.

node.text:
Our birthday is coming up, and we’re celebrating big this year with a look back at our journey! 🎉

Check in daily to find out the sale of the day and fun facts about each year we’ve been around!

In 2015, our story began with a handful of bracelets and a dream. We were founded in Wisconsin back in August of 2015, launching with around 20 stone bracelets.

Last chance to shop 25% off ALL Bracelets today until our next discounted collection tomorrow! ✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Elevated Faith on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Let go of your concerns tonight and give them to God, He's got you 💙
